{"tid":40787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【葉劉選特首】政綱力爭2021年主辦全運會　原來去年10月已截止申辦？","createTime":"2016-12-15T12:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T16:16:56.000Z","uid":30427,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"043997f80cc153874f56205b83cc5c20590cc145","tid":40787,"uid":30427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161215/s00001/1481799936671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161215%2Fs00001%2F1481799936671&d=dmzxkdd1Kkw2ixG9jwRT5KEBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=fcd67484\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161215%2Fs00001%2F1481799936671&h=65306e76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161215/s00001/1481799936671</a><br />\n<br />\n新民黨主席葉劉淑儀宣布，參加下一屆特首選舉。其競選網站已列出9大政綱，當中包括推動文化及體育發展，其中提及「爭取2021年全國運動會於香港舉行，推動體育活動盛事化」，不過，綜合內地媒體廣泛報道，2021年全運會的主辦權早已落於陝西省，而且去年10月31日已是申辦的最後期限。<br />\n<br />\n根據葉劉淑儀政綱，她希望延續政府運動普及化及精英化的大方向，也感受到體育在近年分化及對立的氣氛中，發揮了團結社會的作用。除確保啟德體育園區能夠如期落成，以舉辦不同的國際賽事外，葉劉又提到，要「爭取2021年全國運動會於香港舉行，推動體育活動盛事化」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，原來2021年全運會早已決定由陝西主辦，而且根據國家體育總局2021年全運會申辦流程，去年10月31日已是各省區市遞交申辦報告的最後期限，換言之，假如今日入紙申請，也比截止日期遲了整整1年。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地媒體報道，國務院辦公廳已發函同意陝西省承辦2021年第十四屆全國運動會。函件中提到，籌備和舉辦第14屆全運會的經費，主要由陝西省人民政府自籌，中央財政給予一次性定額補助；場館設施建設所需資金由陝西省人民政府自行負擔。<br />\n<br />\n（新浪體育 / 北京青年報 / 新華社）<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：明報特首選舉專頁<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：葉劉：香港現比何時都更民主 很大證據顯示兩制在一國下運作漸趨穩健<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：葉劉：現階段談班底太早 田北辰搶咪：一定有我<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：田北辰：葉太坦率得可愛、堅持得可敬"},{"pid":"086b354282f91dc2adddc90235a4fd2a045ae94f","tid":40787,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:22:17.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca1d83725cf8d2ecc4fa90d55791942f3b1b65c","tid":40787,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:24:32.000Z","msg":"柒夠未"},{"pid":"4cbc41421bafb8fd90b11170d27b109f448f5616","tid":40787,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8639c81fa7eeac8e2e5f434127a27ea6ad7191b5","tid":40787,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:27:11.000Z","msg":"支那葉出來做小丑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9867e39a69bfd7284754a39642a6c6de3f809df3","tid":40787,"uid":64934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"亡口 <br />\n死淨把口"},{"pid":"8226ed0fe3099c81892006f770aedbb93476481e","tid":40787,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661bdf503d322a38aaac6ff2d75d6afac405e06b","tid":40787,"uid":29295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019fdf3dbe67cd8af479a5d258f1a990f6abb1d9","tid":40787,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:54:09.000Z","msg":"未選到已經走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e922d4b28f2545ef0abb82e896bb331efb565a1c","tid":40787,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"英聯邦運動會下話？"}]}